data.description: Here it is, beautiful 4-2.5-2 with separate dining rm, game room and master bedroom downstairs. Nice kitchen with granite countertops, lots of cabinets and open to the living room.  Upstairs you will find 3 large bedrooms and a nice big game room or 2nd living area whichever you prefer, Good size back yard, corner lot. Easy access to Loop 1604 or Hwy 90. Easy commute to Lackland Air Force Base. Solar panels in place for low utility bills. Don't wait, come see this house today!!
